== What's included? ==

There are several tools for which configuration and customization is provided:

* Shells: [https://www.gnu.org/software/bash/ bash] and [http://www.zsh.org/ zsh] (via 
* Editors: [http://www.vim.org/ Vim]
* SCM tools: [[Git]] and [https://myrepos.branchable.com/ myrepos]

Where possible, configuration is driven by plugin managers:
* [https://github.com/tarjoilija/zgen zgen] and [http://ohmyz.sh/ Oh-My-Zsh] for zsh
* [https://github.com/VundleVim/Vundle.vim Vundle] for vim
